                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Prince
                            <persName type="to">Cantacuzène</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-11-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 6, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>My <hi rend="smallcaps">Dear Prince</hi>: The President and Mrs. Cleveland, the
                    members of his Cabinet and their wives, and Mr. Bayard, our ambassador at
                    London, and his wife, will testify their respect for the memory of the late
                    Emperor by attending the funeral services at your legation on Friday at 10
                    o’clock a.m.</p>
                <p>I have requested the chief of police to call and receive any directions you might
                    desire to make for the occasion.</p>
                <p>Faithfully yours,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">W. Q. Gresham.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
